Let's compute sqrt(97969). 313²=97969, so c=313. 2: a=26, b=144 +24=168, c= sqrt(26² +168²)=sqrt(676 +28224)=sqrt(28900)=170. 3: a=27, b=96 +24=120, c= sqrt(27² +120²)=sqrt(729 +14400)=sqrt(15129)=123. 4: a=28, b=72 +24=96, c= sqrt(28² +96²)=sqrt(784 +9216)=sqrt(10000)=100. 6: a=30, b=48 +24=72, c= sqrt(30² +72²)=sqrt(900 +5184)=sqrt(6084)=78
